      "n": 32,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tahs Durwis bija no\ndiwi Gabbalẽm no Efjes-Roh-\nka/ un wiꞥſch raſtija us teem\nKerubim/ un Palma-Rohkus/ un\natwehru Pukkes/ un pahrwiſke\ntohs ar Seltu/ ir wiꞥſch pahr-\nwilke tohs Kerubim/ un tohs\nPalma-Rohkus ar Seltu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 33,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta darrija wiꞥſch arri/\nkur Deewa Namnã ja-ee-eet\ntschetrkantigus Stabbus no Ef-\njes-Kohkeem/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 34,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tahs Durwis no diwi\nGabbaleem bija no Preedes-\nRohka/ ta ka ikkatram Durwju\nGabbalam diwi Galdi bija/ kas\neekſch faweein Eageem groly-\nfijahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 35,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch iſrakſtija tahs\nar Kerubim/ un Palma-Rohkeem/\nun atwehru Pukkehm/ un pahr-\nwilke tohs ar Seltu/ ittin ka tas\nparwehſchts bija.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 36,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Pehz taifija wiꞥſch to\neekſchoju Pagalmu / no trim\nRindahm apzirſtu Akminu / un\nweenas Rindas Zeedra Balku.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 37,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Zettorta Gaddã tai Meh-\nnesi Siw/ tappe ta KUNGA\nNamna Grunte likta.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 38,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un weenpadeſinita Gad-\ndã tai Mehneſi Bul/ (tas irr tas\nastohts Mehnes/) tappe tas\nNams pabeigts/ ar wiﬀeem fa-\nweem Gabbaleem / un ar wiﬀu\nfawu Baijadsibu/ ta irr wiꞥſch\nfeptians Gaddus pee ta taifijis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Et pee fawa Nam-\ntaisija Salamans tri-\npadeſmits Gaddus/\nmebr wiꞥſch wiﬀu fawu Na-\nnu pabeidſe.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wiꞥſch darrija arrid-\nweenu Namnu no ta Me-\nLihbanus/ ſints Ohleſchu\nwiwa Garrums / un pee-\nmits Ohleſchu bija wiwa Pa-\ntums/ un trihsdeſmits Ohleſ-\nwiwa Augſtums. Us tschetr-\nZeedra Stabbu Rindahm/ un-\nteem Stabbeem bija weena\nbru Grihde.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas bija ar Zeedr-\napſists no Wirfus us tahin Q-\njahm/ kas us tschetreſmits\npeezeem Stabbeem bija/ pee-\ndefmits weena Rindã.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un trihs Lohgu Rin-\nbija/ ta ka weens Lohgs tam-\ntram pretti ſtahweja tre-\nReifês.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ir wiﬀas Durwis un S-\ndext bija tschetreem Kanteen-\nLohgeem/ un weens Lohgs\ntam ohtram pretti tretjas Re-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wiꞥſch darrija arrii-\nweenu Preekſch-Nammnu\n"
    }
  ],
